::KitKat::

She looked at Quickstrike and spoke in a soft, patien voice, trying to 
hold back her temper from him yelling at her."The self destruct 
squence on the base was activated. it's going to blow up in 8 seconds. 
And as to your other question. You will be informed of things as I can 
get around to telling you. Right now we are going to move all our 
equipment and troops to a bigger and better base. I have notifed 
Megatron and Aracnia about our where abouts and they will join us 
shortly."
